188301745237948866.Text: Yes. That makes you the ranking Blades agent here in Vvardenfell district while I'm gone. And I may be gone a while.

2114127706259639893.Text: That makes you the ranking Blades agent here in Vvardenfell district. As far as I know. There may be other Blades agents here I don't know about. It wouldn't surprise me. I may be gone a while, and you'll have expenses. Here's some gold. And you can use the house until I return. And I won't be needing these blacks or the ring while I'm in Cyrodiil. Maybe they'll come in handy. Take good care of them.
